Shipping Policy

We currently ship within the United Kingdom using trusted couriers such as Royal Mail, DPD, and Evri.

Dispatch Times

Orders are typically processed within 24–48 hours (Monday to Friday). Orders placed on weekends or holidays are processed the next working day.

Delivery Times (Estimates)
Standard Delivery: 2–5 business days
Express Delivery: 1–3 business days
Shipping Rates
£3.99 Standard
£7.99 Express
Free shipping on orders £50+
Tracking

You’ll receive an email with tracking details once your order is dispatched (where available).

Delays

Delivery times are estimates and may be affected by courier delays, weather, or peak periods. If your parcel looks delayed, contact us and we will help.